{"tid":1456860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"齊上齊落 四隻大字 有無咁難明","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:14.000Z","uid":15136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40cb6c163eb3245c2af5e2683360ab3ba2fadc91","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"先唔好屌冷氣軍師 散水派 留守派<br />\n係現場既巴絲打如果比人講兩講就走已經好有問題<br />\n其實要做既野由此至終都好簡單<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n你係要走咪托埋隔離個個走<br />\n你要留就說你隔離個個留<br />\n現場未有一個大方向根本就唔應該衝動<br />\n而家走一半留一半 係咪想留/走唔到既人死"},{"pid":"6512cd2e5c6398fa345dab20cbab5b867829a4f7","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:51.000Z","msg":"自推十次開始"},{"pid":"e7b6e05cc309dbc475f5983a8e0a42f16b6e50b3","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"f7c23b7c94038f0761eeb02ef7eed66a09cb1602","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa57d2583477e40d7355f0c8971cf9e4e5ff5c88","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"有無咁難明"},{"pid":"d8c63103a0d4d92d3f5f0a094ac755f41dacb833","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"無人理繼續推"},{"pid":"ca4c39dc7fbf48ac2005d5efa6541e43752fa935","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1b91bf5a9a7c4305017c33f86db40ef9738e534","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"有無手足認同"},{"pid":"dda7dd32f1046155421de58293c7bb3791e8c67a","tid":1456860,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"